setOAuthUser

public void setOAuthUser(java.lang.String user,
                         java.lang.String secret)
Sets the oAuth user which will be used to sign the requests of the current tracker instance. This has to be set explicitly. Please note that, since the tracker is a static instance, requesting a new tracker via getInstance() will not clear the last used oAuth user. To clear the user, use setOAuthUser(null, null);

Parameters:
user -
secret -
